caption.text:
‼️Graphic Content Warning‼️

Didn’t quite start 2022 the way I wanted after having a freak accident in the weight room leading to operations to put my finger back together on Christmas Eve🤠🤠 been getting back into training over the last 4 weeks and indoor season might be postponed but today I got back pole vaulting… even if it’s with one arm for now😝
